 blog is meant to be informative and to have dynamic content, no change control is required','','','','Not required','Thu Feb 09 2017 10:11:30 GMT-1000 (HST)','All external blogs (read only) are here <a href=\"http://www.gemini.edu/blog/\" target=\"_blank\">Blogs</a>'),(7,'4cfe3e21-54f1-4035-94f7-6218f5798bcf','Blog - Internal','Blogs located within Gemini\'s internal site','WordPress','http://blogs.gemini.edu/','If you wish to create a new blog, you can do so via the <a href=\"http://internal.gemini.edu/?q=node/692\" target=\"_blank\">Blog Request Process</a> page. Each blog can only be edited by staff with the correct login and permissions. To gain access to writing on a specific blog, please contact the blog owner','x','All staff can read and comment on internal blogs. To post a blog entry you must request permission to do so from the blog administrator','','Given that blogs are meant to be informative and to have dynamic content, no change control is required','','','','Not required','Tue Jan 31 2017 15:34:00 GMT-1000 (HST)','All internal blogs can be found at <a href=\"http://blogs.gemini.edu/\" target=\"_blank\">BLOGS - Internal</a>'),(8,'71446a69-c5d9-40d9-8955-64147d901f77','Budgets - All','Department level budgets','Control','http://internal.gemini.edu/?q=node/758','To create and view a budget report in Control, please use the <a href=\"http://internal.gemini.edu/?q=node/758\" target=\"_blank\">Monthly Expense Reporting</a> tutorial for further information','x','Access is granted to Budget Managers and restricted to the accounts they manage','','Various scenarios (data) are populated in Control. Actuals and Commitments (POs) are linked to the CAS accounting system and data is verified monthly to be in sync, where each month is then closed. Budget data is created and archived according to the purpose and date created','','','x','Data is reviewed by Finance and Budget managers on a monthly, quarterly and annual basis. Data is also reviewed by the Gemini Board, NSF and External Auditors','Tue Jan 31 2017 15:42:28 GMT-1000 (HST)','Download Control from the <a href=\"http://internal.gemini.edu/?q=node/758\" target=\"_blank\">Control launch pages</a> and then access it through a terminal '),(9,'ce7dbade-395e-45b5-92bd-320592e55714','Charters - Governance/Committees','Defines the Governance/Committee\'s purpose, membership and terms','DMT','http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/View/Collection-79081','Please contact the Executive Assistant for further detail','x','Required. Contact collection owner if you require access','x','Must be approved by the Executive Assistant and Director','','','','Not required','Tue Jan 31 2017 15:44:54 GMT-1000 (HST)','<a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/View/Collection-79081\" target=\"_blank\">Governance Document</a> collection in DMT'),(13,'c82fa4f5-3835-481b-8c71-97a3ec7d7bd0','Charters - Projects','Business / Mission statement, project scope, problem/opportunity statement','DMT','http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/Services/Document-286809','Download the <a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/Services/Document-286809\"  target=\"_blank\">Project Charter DMT Template</a>. See <a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/en/help/user/pdf/user_guide.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">DMT User Guide</a>. Please add metadata (keywords) when adding documents to DMT to optimize search function','','Not required','x','Contact the Project Lead in order to apply changes to the project charter','x','','','Not required','Thu Feb 02 2017 13:18:43 GMT-1000 (HST)','Contact the Project Lead'),(14,'36b5e8cd-0b0e-41a2-ba0c-eda3d1c38809','Code - Software (SW)','Software code','Apache Subversion','','No templates available','x','Required. Contact collection owner if you require access','x','Apache Subversion (SVN) enforces change control','x','','x','Audits are required','Thu Feb 02 2017 13:48:52 GMT-1000 (HST)','Contact the SW group to access non-public code <a href=\"http://drforum.gemini.edu/topic-tag/script/\" target=\"_blank\">Data Reduction Scripts</a>'),(15,'17f75d6e-e1c4-40cb-8f6d-04f5afcb5d9c','Drawings','Drawing schematics','DMT','http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/View/Collection-46622',' All drawings created by contractors must also adhere to the Gemini drawings nomenclature\n<ol>\n<li>Systems Engineering will assign a number block for new systems or instruments as needed\nfollowing the drawings nomenclature, an example of this is 83-YY-2222-3333 (whereby 83\nidentifies the number block, YY identifies the contractor that generated the drawing, 2222\nidentifies the secondary number that represents a particular system or area within each\nprimary group and 3333 represents a unique identification number from 0001 to 9999).</li>\n<li>Once the drawing is ready to be stored upload into the <a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/View/Collection-53951\" target=\"_blank\">New Drawings collection</a></li>\n<li>Drawing will be sent for automatic approval. If approved it will be stored in DMT and added\nto the Master list</li>\n</ol>','','Not required','x','All Gemini staff can access drawings. However, in order to update an\nexisting drawings a user must submit for approval following the steps shown below.\n<ol>\n<li>Obtain the latest version of the drawing from DMT</li>\n<li>Once the drawing is ready to be stored upload into this <a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/View/Collection-53951\" target=\"_blank\">New Drawings collection</a></li>\n<li>Drawing will be sent for automatic approval. If approved it will be stored in DMT and the\nnew version added to the Master list</li>\n</ol>','x','','x','Before any modifications are made or new parts are ordered for an instrument, audits must take place to ensure the current drawings reflects the state of the Gemini system','Thu Feb 02 2017 13:55:30 GMT-1000 (HST)','<a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/Services/Document-327845\" target=\"_blank\">Drawings Master List</a>: list of all drawings stored in DMT'),(16,'488aeee6-e62e-4711-9bb0-b06ed13fbb8a','Fault Reports (Telescope related)','Daily Telescope Fault Reports','JIRA','http://swgserv01.cl.gemini.edu:8080/secure/Dashboard.jspa','Details of how to create a fault report can be found online at the <a href=\"http://internal.gemini.edu/its/?p=1774#Creatingafaultreport\" target=\"_blank\">JIRA Service desk</a>','','Access restrictions to JIRA apply','','JIRA enforces change control','x','','','Not required','Thu Feb 02 2017 14:03:52 GMT-1000 (HST)','Via the <a href=\"http://swgserv01.cl.gemini.edu:8080/secure/Dashboard.jspa\" target=\"_blank\">JIRA dashboard</a>'),(17,'4261dac4-8ca7-45ab-86fd-8828b53f68cb','Governance Committee Meeting Documents','Documents which will be provided prior to the Governance meeting. Located in DMT','DMT','http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/Services/Collection-7982','All Governance report templates and checklists are located in the <a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/Services/Collection-75815\" target=\"_blank\">Governance Committee Meeting Templates and Reports check list</a> collection on DMT. Before uploading any documents to this collection, please contact the collection owner','x','Required. Contact collection owner if you require access','','Not required','','','','Not required','Thu Feb 02 2017 14:11:10 GMT-1000 (HST)','<a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/Services/Collection-7982\" target=\"_blank\">Governance</a> collection in DMT'),(18,'8fecf014-9771-4d5f-90c0-f9f81a86a0f9','Governance Documents','','DMT','http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/View/Collection-72903','All Governance report templates and checklists are located in the <a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/Services/Collection-75815\" target=\"_blank\">Governance Committee Meeting Templates and Reports check list</a> collection on DMT. Before uploading any documents to this collection, please contact the collection owner','x','Required. Contact collection owner if you require access','x','Must be approved by the Executive Assistant and Director','','','','Not required','Thu Feb 02 2017 14:37:15 GMT-1000 (HST)','<a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/View/Collection-72903\" target=\"_blank\">Directorate</a> collection on DMT'),(19,'e62110c9-43c0-4b76-ab58-080f028c0f6d','Interface Control Document (ICD)','A document specifying the interface between one subsystem and another, this includes but is not limited to mechanical, optical, electronic, software, and human interfaces','DMT','http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/View/Collection-7584','Below are the naming conventions that must be honored in order to maintain the integrity of the ICDs Documentation System. Please contact Systems Engineering to assign a number block for new subsystems\n<ol>\n<li>\n<b>System to system: </b> x.x.x/y.y.y\n<ol type=\"a\">\n<li>x.x.x: The first subsystem</li>\n<li>y.y.y: The second subsystem</li>\n<li>Up to three levels of subsystems may be used</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li><b>For reference: </b><a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/Services/Document-275839\" target=\"_blank\">Please use the Interface Control Document Product Tree</a></li>\n<li><b>Systems</b>\n<ol type=\"a\">\n<li>System 1.x.x = Telescope/Instrument Support</li>\n<li>System 2.x.x = Enclosure</li>\n<li>System 3.x.x = Support Facilities</li>\n<li>System 4.x.x = Sea-level Facilities</li>\n<li>General ICDs = All specifications for General ICDs</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li><b>ICD Number Example: </b>1.1.1/1.1.2 Telescope Structure to Encoders</li>\n<li>Please ensure you apply meta tags (keywords) to each ICD when uploading (i.e. project name, subsystem acronym, etc.</li>\n</ol>','','Not required','x','<a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/Services/Document-278412\" target=\"_blank\">User Guide and Updating Procedure</a>','x','','x','Before any modifications are made or new parts are ordered for an instrument, audits must take place to ensure the current ICD reflects the state of the Gemini system.','Thu Feb 02 2017 14:46:26 GMT-1000 (HST)','Located in the <a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/View/Collection-7584\" target=\"_blank\">ICDs and Specifications</a> collection in DMT'),(20,'354c4f81-f75b-4138-be32-9557ff21a0a5','Images - Instrument (non science)','Images relating to instruments','DMT','http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/View/Collection-2195','When uploading images to DMT, please title picture folders with ‘YYYY-MM-DD: [description]’','','Not required','','Not required','x','When uploading images to DMT, please title picture folders with ‘YYYY-MM-DD: [description]’','','Not required','Thu Feb 02 2017 15:32:20 GMT-1000 (HST)','Images are stored in individual collections on <a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/View/Collection-2195\" target=\"_blank\">DMT Instrument Images Collection</a><br />\nNorth: <a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/Services/Collection-2215\" target=\"_blank\">GMOS-N</a>, <a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/Services/Collection-2303\" target=\"_blank\">NIRI</a>, <a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/Services/Collection-2292\" target=\"_blank\">NIFS</a>, <a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/Services/Collection-2237\" target=\"_blank\">GNIRS</a>, <a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/View/Collection-46872\" target=\"_blank\">GCAL</a>, <a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/Services/Collection-21049\" target=\"_blank\">ALTAIR</a>, <a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/View/Collection-46235\" target=\"_blank\">GRACES</a> (visiting), <a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/View/Collection-67410\" target=\"_blank\">TEXES</a> (visiting)<br />\nSouth: <a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/Services/Collection-2226\" target=\"_blank\">GMOS-S</a>, <a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsweb/Services/Collection-2259\" target=\"_blank\">GSAOI</a>, <a href=\"http://dmt.gemini.edu/docushare/dsw